<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="narrow-adj">narrow <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'nærəʊ/    美 /'næroʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(宽度等) 狭窄的</strong></h4>
<p>反 wide </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As we set out, I was shocked at how narrow the path was. 
出发后，我吃惊地发现这条小路是多么狭窄！</p><footer>2008 陕西</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(心胸、视野等) 狭隘的 / 狭窄的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 broad  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>narrow-minded</strong>
心胸狭隘的</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She has a very <strong>narrow view</strong> of the world. 
她的世界观非常狭隘。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[常用于名词前] 勉强的；好不容易的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>narrow victory</strong> 
险胜</p></div></div>